title: Temple of Kylara
story: Kylara is long dead, but people are still afraid to come close to the temple. Lately a terryfying beholder has made its lair here. Rumors say that countless treasures of ancient books can be found here.

notes.text: A scorched double door with a keyhole to the south.
A crystalized body of a halfling, a leather armor and some gold close by.
A battered strongbox with a golden key in it.
A crate holds a strange, unnaturally light shield.
